{"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsProtocol"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"onNotifySettingsSchema","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO11SettingsRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SettingsRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifySettingsSchema"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}],"name":"handler"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::settings-schema"},{"type":"text","text":" signal"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note"}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsProtocol\/onNotifySettingsSchema(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO16SettingsProtocolPAAE08onNotifyB6Schema5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0B3RefV_AG09ParamSpecM0VtctF","title":"onNotifySettingsSchema(flags:handler:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifySettingsSchema","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO11SettingsRefV","text":"SettingsRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s: